data.description:
Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to own a charming 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with a 1-car garage! With a brand new roof set to be installed before closing, this residence offers peace of mind and security for years to come.

 

Boasting 1,292 square feet of living space, this home has been thoughtfully updated with vinyl plank flooring throughout, as well as fresh interior and exterior paint. Step inside to discover a bright and airy open living area, perfect for relaxing or entertaining.

 

The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring wooden cabinets, granite counters, stainless steel appliances, and a convenient breakfast bar. Just off the kitchen, you'll find the dining room, ideal for enjoying meals with family and friends.

 

Down the hallway, you'll find the guest bathroom with a newer single sink vanity and a tub/shower combo with tile surround. The first bedroom, complete with a ceiling fan and large closet, offers tranquil views of the fenced-in rear yard.

 

The master bedroom is a peaceful retreat, featuring a walk-in closet and an ensuite bathroom with a single sink vanity and fully tiled walk-in shower.

 

With its desirable features and prime location, this home is sure to go quickly. Schedule your appointment today and make it yours before it's too late!
